metadata.name: MAKO - the White Tigress
metadata.description:
She has been in many places, has seen many things, heard and learned a lot from different people. Being a nomad isn't a problem for Mako. In fact, she enjoys wandering here and there. She's very compassionate towards elderly people and orphans.
Despite her warm character, Mako is a hired assassin that is known for her agility and brutal execution, a few traits imbued by her Seishin, a celestial White Tiger.
Just one knock at her door plus a good amount of gold, and she's ready to pounce.


[2160 x 3840 px]
